					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12187050#post-4298492</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12187050/scp-4792#post-4298492</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2019 05:43:17 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Yossipossi</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2199269</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <blockquote> <p>&quot;<em>I have seen the dark universe yawning</em><br /> <em>Where the black planets roll without aim,</em><br /> <em>Where they roll in their horror unheeded,</em><br /> <em>Without knowledge, or lustre, or name.</em>&quot;</p> <p>–H.P. Lovecraft, Nemesis</p> </blockquote> </div> <p>Thanks for reading this article!</p> <p>The concept was primarily an original idea, though was partially inspired by <a href="https://stellaris.paradoxwikis.com/Crisis#The_Contingency">The Contingency</a> from Stellaris. Image is from <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:HD_108147-starmap.png">here</a></p> <p>Credits to people who helped with the skip:</p> <ul> <li><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1414765&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562307757" alt="Doctor Cimmerian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1414765)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" >Doctor Cimmerian</a></span>:</strong> For helping me refine the concept from its initial development stage and spending hours in voice chat ranting about Dyson spheres.</li> <li><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562307757" alt="FloppyPhoenix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" >FloppyPhoenix</a></span>:</strong> For assisting in idea refinement, helping with N E R D stuffs, and also providing useful critique.</li> <li><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/validclay" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4538622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1562307757" alt="ValidClay" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4538622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/validclay" >ValidClay</a></span>:</strong> For giving me incredibly good critique for the concept and execution.</li> <li>And also a number of other users for providing critique!</li> </ul> <p>Thanks for stopping by, have a good day!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
